description: Available now is this spacious two-bedroom unit with deeded, off-street parking. Snow removal included! This home features tall ceilings, an updated kitchen, 1.5 bathrooms, central air conditioning, a Nest thermostat, all hardwood flooring and convenient in-unit laundry. Located just around the corner from the Broadway T station on the Red Line, this unit is perfect for commuters with quick access to both I-90 and I-93 as well as South Station/Amtrak, the Seaport District and Logan Airport. Each bedroom is a great size and they are located on opposite sides of the unit for enhanced privacy. You will want to entertain your guests in the open living space that is large enough for a dining table and adjacent to the striking kitchen complete with stainless appliances, granite counters and gas cooking. There is also room for a home office! The location could not be better, with your favorite restaurants, shops and bars close by.
